    "body": "<!-- Thank you for your contribution! Please follow these guidelines to enhance your pull request. If anything is unclear, submit your PR and reach out to maintainers for assistance. Join our Slack community at https://slack.sglang.ai to discuss further. -->\r\nco-authored by @elfiegg \r\n## Motivation\r\nDepends on [10459](https://github.com/sgl-project/sglang/pull/10459). This PR is supposed to be merged after 10459. This PR enables TRTLLM_MLA backend for chunked prefix cache extend. There is a issue with the kernel that might write out-of-bound for such case:\r\n```\r\nactual_seq_lens_kv:tensor([1280,    0])\r\n```\r\nComparing the corresponding lse from flashinfer cutlass backend and trtllm_mla:\r\n```\r\nlse by trtllm_mla: tensor([[18.0920, 10.1281, 15.6364,  ..., 10.2854, 11.6327, 12.3531],\r\n        [17.1094, 12.4606, 13.9145,  ...,  8.4001, 12.3192, 12.4203],\r\n        [18.6047, 13.0789, 14.4112,  ...,  8.5011, 13.0588, 11.7544],\r\n        ...,\r\n        [14.4315,  7.8263,  6.7507,  ...,  7.1547,  5.4750,  8.9328],\r\n        [14.9907,  9.6778,  7.0009,  ...,  6.7419,  5.5235,  8.1809],\r\n        [12.5050,  8.2411,  6.8862,  ...,  6.2882,  5.9210,  7.7119]],\r\n       device='cuda:1')\r\nlse by flashinfer cutlass: tensor([[18.0920, 10.1281, 15.6364,  ..., 10.2854, 11.6327, 12.3531],\r\n        [17.1094, 12.4606, 13.9145,  ...,  8.4001, 12.3192, 12.4203],\r\n        [18.6047, 13.0789, 14.4112,  ...,  8.5011, 13.0588, 11.7544],\r\n        ...,\r\n        [   -inf,    -inf,    -inf,  ...,    -inf,    -inf,    -inf],\r\n        [   -inf,    -inf,    -inf,  ...,    -inf,    -inf,    -inf],\r\n        [   -inf,    -inf,    -inf,  ...,    -inf,    -inf,    -inf]],\r\n       device='cuda:1')\r\n```\r\nThe expected value should be -inf. It also affects the output from the kernel that the oom position should hold 0.\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\n<!-- Detail the changes made in this pull request. -->\r\n\r\n## Accuracy Tests\r\n\r\n```\r\nserver.sh\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\r\n  --model-path nvidia/DeepSeek-R1-0528-FP4 \\\r\n  --trust-remote-code \\\r\n  --disable-radix-cache \\\r\n  --max-running-requests 256 \\\r\n  --chunked-prefill-size 2048 \\\r\n  --mem-fraction-static 0.89 \\\r\n  --max-prefill-tokens 32768 \\\r\n  --attention-backend trtllm_mla \\\r\n  --disable-cuda-graph \\\r\n  --tp 8 \\\r\n  --dp 8 \\\r\n  --enable-dp-attention \\\r\n  --quantization modelopt_fp4\r\n\r\nclient:\r\n python3 benchmark/gsm8k/bench_sglang.py --num-shots 8 --num-questions 1310 --parallel 1310\r\n \r\nAccuracy: 0.951\r\nInvalid: 0.001\r\nLatency: 332.156 s\r\nOutput throughput: 433.811 token/s\r\n\r\n```\r\n## Benchmarking and Profiling\r\n\r\n```\r\nserver:\r\npython3 -m sglang.launch_server \\\r\n  --model-path nvidia/DeepSeek-R1-0528-FP4 \\\r\n  --trust-remote-code \\\r\n  --disable-radix-cache \\\r\n  --max-running-requests 256 \\\r\n  --chunked-prefill-size 2048 \\\r\n  --mem-fraction-static 0.89 \\\r\n  --max-prefill-tokens 32768 \\\r\n  --attention-backend trtllm_mla \\\r\n  --disable-cuda-graph \\\r\n  --tp 8 \\\r\n  --dp 8 \\\r\n  --enable-dp-attention \\\r\n  --quantization modelopt_fp4\r\n  \r\nclient\r\npython3 -m sglang.bench_serving  --model nvidia/DeepSeek-R1-0528-FP4 --dataset-name random  --backend sglang-oai  --random-range-ratio 1  --random-input-len 8192 --random-output-len 2 --max-concurrency 256  --num-prompts 512 \r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang-oai\r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf\r\nMax request concurrency:                 256\r\nSuccessful requests:                     512\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  302.17\r\nTotal input tokens:                      4194304\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  51200\r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    50751\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.69\r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          13880.41\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         169.44\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          14049.85\r\nConcurrency:                             255.92\r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   151041.88\r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 151041.23\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          75479.20\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        75264.00\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           147527.45\r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           768.35\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         51.01\r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            55.53\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            448.38\r\nMax ITL (ms):                            141254.31\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n```\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang-oai\r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf\r\nMax request concurrency:                 256\r\nSuccessful requests:                     512\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  298.38\r\nTotal input tokens:                      4194304\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  1024\r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    1013\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.72\r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          14056.75\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         3.43\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          14060.19\r\nConcurrency:                             255.90\r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   149134.68\r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 149115.82\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          77065.87\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        76854.22\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           150200.41\r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           72253.20\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         72892.67\r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            137683.22\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            144372.70\r\nMax ITL (ms):                            144470.13\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n\r\nlow latency:\r\nmax-concurrency 4 num-prompts 128\r\nbefore:\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang-oai\r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf\r\nMax request concurrency:                 4\r\nSuccessful requests:                     128\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  131.21\r\nTotal input tokens:                      1048576\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  256\r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    256\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              0.98\r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          7991.75\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         1.95\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          7993.70\r\nConcurrency:                             4.00\r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   4096.73\r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 3884.56\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          3939.99\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        3786.54\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           5996.81\r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           156.73\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         101.72\r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            1042.14\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            1086.76\r\nMax ITL (ms):                            1102.26\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nafter\r\n============ Serving Benchmark Result ============\r\nBackend:                                 sglang-oai\r\nTraffic request rate:                    inf\r\nMax request concurrency:                 4\r\nSuccessful requests:                     128\r\nBenchmark duration (s):                  123.00\r\nTotal input tokens:                      1048576\r\nTotal generated tokens:                  256\r\nTotal generated tokens (retokenized):    256\r\nRequest throughput (req/s):              1.04\r\nInput token throughput (tok/s):          8525.21\r\nOutput token throughput (tok/s):         2.08\r\nTotal token throughput (tok/s):          8527.30\r\nConcurrency:                             4.00\r\n----------------End-to-End Latency----------------\r\nMean E2E Latency (ms):                   3841.53\r\nMedian E2E Latency (ms):                 3815.65\r\n---------------Time to First Token----------------\r\nMean TTFT (ms):                          3753.17\r\nMedian TTFT (ms):                        3735.32\r\nP99 TTFT (ms):                           4735.72\r\n---------------Inter-Token Latency----------------\r\nMean ITL (ms):                           88.35\r\nMedian ITL (ms):                         75.78\r\nP95 ITL (ms):                            119.53\r\nP99 ITL (ms):                            120.13\r\nMax ITL (ms):                            1025.67\r\n==================================================\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [ ] Format your code according to the [Format code with pre-commit](https://docs.sglang.ai/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#format-code-with-pre-commit).\r\n- [ ] Add unit tests according to the [Run and add unit tests](https://docs.sglang.ai/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#run-and-add-unit-tests).\r\n- [ ] Update documentation according to [Write documentations](https://docs.sglang.ai/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#write-documentations).\r\n- [ ] Provide accuracy and speed benchmark results according to [Test the accuracy](https://docs.sglang.ai/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#test-the-accuracy) and [Benchmark the speed](https://docs.sglang.ai/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#benchmark-the-speed).\r\n",
